name: Sunnyside Up
overview: Sunnyside Up was a weekly variety program produced at HSV-7 Melbourne, during the late 1950s and early 1960s.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: Rhyme from Chicken Girls puts her writer's cap on to create a fictional story called Sunnyside Up. The story follows Lily, and her newfound friends as they form an unconventional girl gang on Sunnyside Court. The girls attend a wacky new age high school where all kinds of fantastical, colorful characters come to play -- and where the tea never stops flowing.

episodes.name: The Fascinator Hat
episodes.overview: Lily might be the new kid on the block at Sunnyside Court, but her attitude is far from sunny. Will she find her place and make new friends or will the resident mean girls only add to the cloud above her head?

episodes.name: The Dosimeter Pencil
episodes.overview: At Sunnyside Court, everyone is stepping out of their comfort zones. Avery tries to fit in, Mila goes against her fathers' wishes, and Lily does her best to make do in yet another new school.

episodes.name: The Kaleidoscope
episodes.overview: Mila and Lily prepare for the C.U.D.D.L.E. science fair, while Avery continues to try and fit in with the popular kids...that is, until *someone* steps in with a little advice.

episodes.name: The Chess Set
episodes.overview: Lily tries to teach Pearl a lesson by threatening to expose her secret hobby. Meanwhile, Mila decides to reject her dads' strict schedule for her... by going on a date.

episodes.name: The Postcard
episodes.overview: After getting in trouble with her dads, Mila tries her best to regain their trust. Meanwhile, Pearl's popular girl posse does their best to squash Lily and Avery's budding friendship... but will they succeed?

episodes.name: The Egyptian Cotton
episodes.overview: Lily does her best to keep her new friends happy, but will Avery uncover an ulterior motive behind her kindness....?

episodes.name: The Package
episodes.overview: It's time for the C.U.D.D.L.E. science fair! But, it seems the biggest reactions are anything but scientific...

episodes.name: The Chocolate Nobel Prize
episodes.overview: As the semester (and the season) comes to a close, Lily makes a last ditch effort to bring everyone back together on Sunnyside Court.
